thai beverage public company limited  สงวนลิขสิทธิ์  บริษัท ไทยเบฟเวอเรจ จำกัด มหาชน thai beverage public company limited   search      thbev price   corporate profile our vision message from chairman vision  business overview management structure awards media corporate governance report annual report brewery group distiller group related business group marketing group international business group sale group nonalcohol beverage business group sole agent group group of listed companies on the stock exchange of thailand trademark group others beer spirits non  alcohol beverage related business oishi chilled  frozen foods international product portfolio         apart from liquor and beer products companies with in the group of the thai beverage plc also have several other related products they are established with the aim to produce and market products realized from waste materials in order to add value help reduce waste matters but at the same time are also the initiators of technical researches that directly benefit the general public these products are light construction bricks fertilizers from liquor production wastes animal feed and supplementary animal feed from malt waste etc         chang beer   chang is a lager beer with a pleasant full flavour subtle fruit and hop aroma delivering a natural easytodrink brew chang classic product type lager beer major ingredient contents from fine quality malt rice and hop with natural water and selected yeast especially for chang beer alcohol content  by volume color bottle emerald green type of content bottle  ml and  ml can  ml and  ml contain in cases big bottle  ml  bottlescase small bottlecan  ml  bottlescase  can  ml case brewery  cosmos brewery thailand co ltd  beer thip brewery  co ltd  beer thai  plc archa beer archa beer was first launched in july  to expand the market share particularly in the standard and premium product groups and to respond to increasing demands from a new generation of beer drinkers who prefer smooth beer with lower alcohol content archa beer thus serves as another alternative for beer drinkers   product type lager beer major ingredient contents from fine quality malt rice and hop with natural water and selected yeast especially for archa beer alcohol content  by volume color amber gold type of content bottle  ml can  ml contain in cases big bottle  ml  bottlescase can  ml case brewery  beerthip brewery  co ltd  beer thai  plc    federbräu is a german inspired quality beer brewed using the finest imported german malt using only a single source of german malt in the brewing process federbräu offers a uniquely german beer experience that is easy to drink and refreshing with  abv federbräu is a smooth tasting authentic german beer flavor   product type lager beer major ingredient contents from fine quality malt hop with natural water and selected yeast especially for alcohol content  by volume color bottle amber gold type of content bottle ml and ml can ml contain in cases big bottle ml  bottlescase small bottle ml  bottlescase can ml  canscase brewery the cosmos brewery thailand company limited as of march           thai beverage public company limited           about us corporate profile our vision message from chairman vision  business overview management structure awards media corporate governance report annual report business groups brewery group distillery group related business group marketing group international business group sale group nonalcohol beverage business group sole agent group group of listed companies on the stock exchange of thailand trademark group others product groups beer spirits nonalcohol beverage related business japanese restaurants international product portfolio     thaibev news spacial news thaibev news social responsibility thailand foundation sustainability report thaibev policies gri g content index and un sustainable development goals download the fullsustainability report  investor relations thaibev infomercials thaibev…