ivadhanabhakdi headquarters bangkok thailand area served worldwide key people thapana sirivadhanabhakdi president and ceo revenue  billion baht   profit  billion baht   total assets  billion baht   subsidiaries fraser and neave sermsuk oishi group interbev group website wwwthaibevcom thai beverage better known as thaibev thai ไทยเบฟ sgx y is thailands largest and one of southeast asias largest beverage companies with distilleries in thailand scotland ireland china and france listed on the singapore stock exchange thai beverage plc has a market capitalization in excess of us billion in january  the firm announced it had succeeded in a us billion deal to take over the conglomerate fraser and neave adding to the groups considerable portfolio of assets contents  overview  beer  changcarlsberg history  spirits  production  evertonchang  criticism and protest  see also  notes  references  external links overviewedit thapana sirivadhanabhakdi company president and ceo thai beverage public company limited owns and distributes several significant brands including chang beer mekhongand sangsom rum it also has significant operations in europe producing malt scotch whisky vodka gin and liqueurs with over  distilleries in scotland france poland and ireland mr charoen sirivadhanabhakdi in early  added fraser and neave limited a food and beverage brewing property and publishing industries conglomerate in singapore to his drinks and property empire chang beer which started production in march  at their brewery in bang ban district of ayutthaya province is the topselling brand in thailand it managed to win  percent market share in thailand after a hard market fight with the previous leading brand singha in  the companys beer market share was  percent according to research company canadean beeredit a bottle of chang beer thaibev brews chang or chang beer thai เบียร์ช้าง a pale lager chang thai ช้าง is the thai word for elephant an animal with cultural and historical significance in thailand the logo features two elephants facing each other in  the company introduced archa beer at  percent abv archa won a gold medal at the  australian international beer awards aiba the abv was lowered to  percent in  the first market outside thailand to distribute archa beer was singapore and it was successfully launched in singapore back in  by interbev singapore ltd in  the company launched chang light  percent abv and chang draught in bottles at five percent abv they were discontinued in citation needed thaibevs flagship brand chang beer won a gold quality award three times in the beers water and soft drinks category at the world quality selections organized each year by monde selection in  thaibev consolidated all brands into chang classic thaibev stopped production of archa chang beer chang draught and chang export production of chang classic is shared between thaibev’s three breweries the recipe was changed to include rice previously only used in the domestic  version the abv varies between  and  abv depending on the market changcarlsberg historyedit in december  carlsberg and chang established a  joint venture carlsberg asia to create a significant brewing company in asia the carlsberg influence can be seen in the typography of the beer chang logo which resembles the classic carlsberg beer in  carlsberg pulled out of the venture and terminated its licence agreement with chang due to nonfulfillment of contractual obligations resulting in chang claiming us billion in damages a final settlement of us million was subsequently paid by carlsbergcitation needed spiritsedit thaibev produces brown and white spirits including rum which is derived from distilling cane juice sugar or molasses until the product is with – alcohol content the content is mixed with purified water to produce a satisfactory level of alcohol content before being transferred to age in charred oak barrels for at least one year before being bottled the liquor may be further mixed to adjust for