ness consists of four segments  spirits beer nonalcoholic beverage and food thaibev listed on the mainboard of the singapore exchange in  the market cap of thaibev is currently over s  billion in  thaibev expanded its business overseas and through the acquisition of fraser and neave limited a highly recognized company in singapore with a portfolio that boasts many renowned brands thaibev has become the leading beverage producer and distributor in the asean region product or services thaibev has  subsidiaries as of  december  including  distilleries  breweries and  nonalcohol beverage production facilities the group has an extensive distribution network covering  points of sales in thailand thaibevs most recognized spirits brands include ruang khao sangsom mekhong hong thong and blend  chang beer the groups signature beer is very popular among thai beer drinkers for nonalcoholic beverages thaibevs leading brands includes oishi green tea est cola and crystal drinking water thaibev has an international presence in  countries and engages in several distillery operations overseas it has  production facilities in scotland which are famous for the production of single malt scotch whiskies such as balblair old pulteney and speyburn thaibev also owns  distillery in china which produces a famous chinese spirit branded yulinquan investment highlights one of the largest beverage players in asia strong free cash flow  baht  million  ranked among the top  largest companies by market cap in sgx  s  million as of  march  dividend payout not less than  of net profit after deduction of all specified reserves payout ratio    subject to our investment plans and as the board of directors deems appropriate business portfolio   copyright   securities investors association singapore all rights reserved this website is a production of sias reproduction in any form or medium without written permission of sias is prohibited internet service powered by skydio pte ltd thai beverage public compa